# ShopjoyBoApp — Capacitor (Node + Android + iOS)

# ----- Node -----
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.pnpm-debug.log*
package-lock.json.bak

# ----- Capacitor 캐시 -----
.capacitor/
.cap/

# ----- 웹 자산 빌드 결과 -----
www/build/
www/dist/

